name: Tribes: Pimp Gang Hoodie
description:
We heard you're bored and love to ape. Introducing the second drop of the Apesthetics x MetaFactory Tribes Series. All animals of the NFT kingdom are welcome. This drop is open to all Hypebeast JPG fans out there. We are an inclusive family at Apesthetics x Metafactory.
Each physical hoodie comes installed with a SiLo Kong chip for proof of authenticity, your physical products deserve smart contracts too. You can also anticipate an ERC-1155 NFT of the featured backside artwork and a future 3D wearable to rep in the metaverse.
